import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    average_yield_per_site = data.groupby('site')['yield'].mean().reset_index()
    chart = sns.barplot(x='site', y='yield', data=average_yield_per_site)
    plt.title('What is the average yield per site?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Site')
    plt.ylabel('Average Yield')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.boxplot(x='variety', y='yield', data=data)
    plt.title('How does the yield vary by variety?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Variety')
    plt.ylabel('Yield')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend(title='Variety', loc='upper right')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    data['year'] = data['year'].dt.year

    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='year', y='yield', hue='variety', data=data)
    plt.title('What is the trend of yield over the years?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend(title='Variety', loc='upper left')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='yield', hue='site', multiple='stack', legend=True)
    plt.title('What is the distribution of yield across all sites?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Yield')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend(title='Site', loc='upper right')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    pivot_data = data.pivot_table(index='site', columns='variety', values='yield', aggfunc='mean')
    heatmap = sns.heatmap(pivot_data, cmap='coolwarm', annot=True, fmt=".2f")
    plt.title('How does the yield vary by site and variety?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Variety')
    plt.ylabel('Site')
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
